headline: Carrier to Present at Morgan Stanley's 13th Annual Laguna Conference
summary: Carrier Global Corporation (NYSE: CARR) Chairman & CEO David Gitlin and Senior Vice President & CFO Patrick Goris will speak at the 13th Annual Morgan Stanley Laguna Conference on Wednesday, September 10, 2025, at 10:45 a.m. PT (1:45 p.m. ET).
